    title: 'YouTube Shorts Algorithm Explained — How to Go Viral in 2026',
    excerpt:
      'A deep dive into how the YouTube Shorts algorithm works in 2026, including ranking signals, the Shorts shelf, best practices for going viral, and optimal posting strategies.',
    author: 'TubeForge Team',
